profile:
Painterfast is committed to taking the pain out of painting for both the client and the painter. Our painters consist of Painterfast employees and and sub-contractors all of whom are fully insured and have WSIB coverage. If we are using a sub-contractor we accept payment on their behalf and ensure you are 100% happy with the work before full payment is made.

We also ensure that our painters are paid even if we are not.

This provides the best results all around! 100% satisfaction guaranteed EVERY TIME.
